{"word":"G1846 - ἐξορύσσω - exorýssō - ex-or-oos'-so - Break up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξορύσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exorýssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-or-oos'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Break up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிடுங்கு, பிரி"},{"paragraph":"to dig out, to dig through"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G3736 - ὀρύσσω - orýssō - or-oos'-so/3736\">G3736</a>; to <i>dig out</i>, that is, (by extension) to <i>extract</i> (an eye), <i>remove</i> (a roofing): - break up, pluck out.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}